[NAME]
note - attach, display, or remove a user note on a file

[DESCRIPTION]
The 'note' command uses extended file attributes to associate a single
string note with a file. It allows for easy annotation and retrieval of file metadata.

[EXAMPLES]
Add a note:
  note add file.txt "Reviewed by Eric"

Show a note:
  note show file.txt

Remove a note:
  note remove file.txt

